value: Lower Amaz. Brazil s of R. Amazon; single record for nw Bolivia
Northern Bolivia in Department of La Paz (Reyes); Brazil south of the Amazon on the upper Rio Madeira and tributaries (Rio Gi-Parana; Rio Preto), the Rio Tapajoz and the Rio Tocantins. 1
